276
00:18:39,131 --> 00:18:40,534
Mrs. Merkle, you mean.

277
00:18:40,599 --> 00:18:43,170
That's what he said, Mrs. Miracle.

278
00:18:43,234 --> 00:18:44,570
And you know what else?

279
00:18:44,636 --> 00:18:48,242
