A little time for yourself.

293
00:19:28,345 --> 00:19:32,119
What is that? l don't even think about that.

294
00:19:32,184 --> 00:19:34,154
Of course you don't.

295
00:19:34,953 --> 00:19:38,159
You know, l'm sorry.
l didn't even show you to your room.

296
00:19:38,222 --> 00:19:40,627
No, it's all right. The boys settled me in.

297
00:19:40,692 --> 00:19:41,827
-Yeah?
-Yeah.

298
00:19:41,893 --> 00:19:43,763
Okay. Well, then,
l guess we should probably talk

299
00:19:43,828 --> 00:19:47,334
about references, and schedules,
and all that stuff.

300
00:19:47,398 --> 00:19:50,504
Mrs. Miracle! Come on! We're waiting!

301
00:19:50,568 --> 00:19:52,171
