329
00:22:50,514 --> 00:22:54,855
And the angel said unto him, ''Fear not!

330
00:22:54,918 --> 00:23:00,696
''For behold,
l bring you good tidings of great joy!''

331
00:23:13,771 --> 00:23:15,508
ls she okay?

332
00:23:16,273 --> 00:23:19,345
