405
00:28:27,283 --> 00:28:31,157
-Mrs. Merkle, l would appreciate it if...
-What was her name?

406
00:28:31,887 --> 00:28:33,322
Pamela.

407
00:28:35,391 --> 00:28:37,896
Her name was Pamela.

408
00:28:37,960 --> 00:28:40,564
