00:35:12,252 --> 00:35:14,824
And l mean, people like that.

481
00:35:14,889 --> 00:35:18,161
That separates us
from the animals, you know?

482
00:35:18,225 --> 00:35:20,329
l got distracted.

483
00:35:20,394 --> 00:35:22,296
He banged his leg.

